---
title: Spiced Sweet Potato Soup with kidney beans and coconut milk
description: This lightly spiced and hearty sweet potato soup is like a warm hug in a bowl. As an added bonus, it's also filled with flavour, packed with protein, and perfectly plant-based. A dish that well and truly has it all!
